\fs36 \cf0 This story takes place in the future, year 6060, at a time when humans are struggling to survive.  All children are required to take tests, those that score highly are chosen to become wizards.  Most wizards come from parents who are also wizards, but occasionally wizards were chosen from non-wizard families.  This is a story about one of those very \'93special\'94 kids\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85\'85.\
