\f1\i0\b \cf0 I\
Chapter one\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\fi720\sl420\partightenfactor0
\cf0 In order to understand this tale, one must first understand the meaning of the word \'93wizard\'94, as it is used here. A wizard is a highly intelligent human. Wizards have a great deal of power and privileges not granted to ordinary citizens.  The main character of this story, a young boy named Tally, has coffee dark brown - hair, emerald green eyes, a scar, and always wears a necklace with a pearl white stone on it.  But enough of that; to the story: \
\
\'93Owww!\'94\
Tally jumped up and down holding his foot. He had stubbed his toe on his green stone science table. Angry, he kicked the table over and jumped some more. He noticed that none of his metal vials had moved off the table in which he had kicked over, and none of the potions in those vials had spilled out.\
\'93It worked!\'94 yelled Tally.\
He moved forward.  \'93Owwwwwwww!!!\'94\
Tally\'92s foot filled with pain.  He had been working on a potion to made things stick together.  He had previously applied some on his vials, and to see it work filled him with joy.  He was glad that none of his potions were ruined.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	\'93Time for school,\'94 his mother yelled.\
	\'93Just a little longer,\'94 said Tally.  \'93I\'92m going my way.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\fi720\sl420\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Tally\'92s way was underground transportation. One might think that Tally would get straight A\'92s, because of his creations, but he could barely make straight C\'92s.  He had flunked twice. He wanted to get a wizard\'92s degree in potion making, but he knew he couldn\'92t do it.\
At school, it was grade day, so the day hardly had a minute of school in it. The teacher handed grades out, said \'94You may go now\'94 and then school was out.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	After he was dismissed Tally went home. \
	\'93Mom, I passed,\'94 Tally said.\
	\'93Very good,\'94 said his mom.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\qc\partightenfactor0
